    "In short, the choice of fairness metric matters a lot, and without any information on this choice it is hard to say whether the algorithm meets non-discrimination standards.",
    "How does this stack up to the transparency requirements based on the goal of establishing legitimacy?",
    "First, this example has taken a more socio-technical approach to transparency as human oversight is explicitly included in the reported features of the system.",
